node.text:
I’m officially partnering with @NeedForSpeed for the launch of their new game ‘Need for Speed: Heat’  #EAambassador In celebration of this partnership I’m giving all of you a chance to submit custom wrap designs for my new @Mercedesbenzusa AMG GTR 💨💨💨 #NFSHeat

To Design:
•Download the NFS Heat Studio App *Link In Bio*
•Design your wrap on the @mercedesbenz AMG GTR
•Send me your design via IG or Twitter using #NFSHeat and tag @nigelsylvester •I’ll pick my favorite design on Oct. 18 and bring it to life in Miami!

#EAambassador 🎥: @sureshgordon @harrisonboyce @danivanessa @samegangsafe

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by nigelsylvester on July 13, 2021 tagging @hyperice, and @steinbergsports. May be an image of ‎1 person, sitting and ‎text that says '‎ไه businesswire BERKSHIRE HATHAWAY COMPANY Log In Sign Up Nigel Sylvester Joins Hyperice as Global Ambassador Professional BMX Athlete to Design a Recovery Room at High School Alma Mater in Queens, NY‎'‎‎.

node.text:
I’ve officially signed a Global Ambassador partnership with @hyperice. Proper recovery is one of the most important elements to my longevity as a BMX athlete. I’m excited to join the Hyperice family, elevate my recovery regimen and work together to give back to my community. 

To kick off this partnership, @hyperice and I, will be donating and constructing a customized recovery room to my Alma Mater, Benjamin Cardozo High School in Queens, NY, for the health and well-being of the students and faculty. 

#TeamHyperice

node.text:
It’s been a dream of mine to make this a reality, and today we officially launched the Nigel Sylvester Foundation. The @nigelfoundation aims to help transform the lives of youth and unify diverse communities around the world through the shared tradition of bicycling.

BMX riding has changed my life. I believe the bicycle is one of the most powerful and accessible modes of transportation in the world. Through our work, I’ll share how a bicycle has empowered me and spread encouragement and inspiration to underserved communities and youth.

Special thanks to @goodmorningamerica For having having us! @steinbergsports @chriscabott @coachcharities @cyclekids & @iamspecialized 

Nigel Sylvester Foundation - LINK IN BIO

Photo: @ralphyramos
